}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:5:"Diana";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:35926:"\n<p>This post has narrowed down the list to present you 20 of the Best Gutenberg WordPress Themes right now. Gutenberg is the new content creator and editor added to WordPress 5.0. It is an editor that uses blocks to create all types of content, replacing a half-dozen inconsistent ways of customizing WordPress, bringing it in line with modern coding standards, and aligning with open web initiatives. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are planning on building a new website, we recommend you to choose a WordPress theme that’s compatible with WordPress 5.0 and Gutenberg. Here you will find the best Gutenberg WordPress themes you can buy for different kind of domains, just grab one and build your dream website.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Studio 8</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class="wp-block-image shadow"><img src="https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/studio-8-agency-wordpress-theme.jpg" alt="Studio 8 WordPress Theme for Agency, Photographs" class="wp-image-23634" srcset="https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/studio-8-agency-wordpress-theme.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/studio-8-agency-wordpress-theme-300x278.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/studio-8-agency-wordpress-theme-768x711.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/studio-8-agency-wordpress-theme-1024x948.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/studio-8-agency-wordpress-theme-600x556.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /><figcaption>Studio 8 WordPress Theme for Agency, Photographs</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Studio 8 WordPress Theme is one of the best theme on the market, it&#8217;s very popular and loved by Creative People around the world. Studio 8 is a flexible, appealing and profoundly functional theme designed for Creative Professionals, Agencies, Architects, Web Designers, and Filmmakers. The theme has an attractive and professional layout and as you scroll through Studio 8, you will note the various ways you can promote your agency’s services and build credibility with potential clients.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4><strong>The theme is coming with 11 Gutenberg Blocks</strong></h4>\n\n\n\n<div class="wp-block-columns has-3-columns">\n<div class="wp-block-column">\n<ul><li>Accordion</li><li>Alert</li><li>Carousel</li><li>Text Container</li></ul>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class="wp-block-column">\n<ul><li>Container</li><li>Link</li><li>Team</li><li>Pricing Table</li></ul>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class="wp-block-column">\n<ul><li>Projects</li><li>Posts</li><li>Featured Posts</li><li>More to come…</li></ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<p>This theme will hook your visitors and make them stay on your website for extended periods. Studio 8 is Multilingual Ready to cater to your non-English speaking audience. This theme is fully responsive and compatible with Gutenberg and all devices and browsers. Take advantage of the Unlimited Color Schemes to pick a color that is consistent with your brand’s identity. Installation takes just about 3 minutes.</p>\n\n\n\n<a href="https://wplook.com/product/themes/business/studio-8-agency-wordpress-theme/" target="_blank" class="button green-button">Learn More about Studio 8</a>\n<a href="https://wplook.com/createa-a-wordpress-site/?utm_source=post&amp;utm_medium=link&amp;utm_campaign=get_theme_free" class="button pink-button" title="Get this theme for FREE">Get this theme for FREE</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>The Architect</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class="wp-block-image shadow"><img src="https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/thearchitect-website.jpg" alt="The Architect WordPress Theme for Architects" class="wp-image-23640" srcset="https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/thearchitect-website.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/thearchitect-website-300x278.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/thearchitect-website-768x711.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/thearchitect-website-1024x948.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/thearchitect-website-600x556.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /><figcaption>The Architect WordPress Theme for Architects</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Another beautiful theme from our list of Best Gutenberg WordPress Themes is The Architect. This theme will definitely help you impress visitors to your site. Features of this theme include an eye-catching portfolio, gorgeous and clean design, blog page to feature news related to your work, retina support for modern devices, multiple widget areas and unlimited color schemes. Every package you choose with this theme comes with support and updates as well. It also comes with child theme and documentation.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4><strong>The&nbsp;theme&nbsp;is&nbsp;coming&nbsp;with&nbsp;10 Gutenberg Blocks</strong></h4>\n\n\n\n<div class="wp-block-columns has-3-columns">\n<div class="wp-block-column">\n<ul><li>Accordion</li><li>Alert</li><li>Text Container</li><li>Pricing Table</li></ul>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class="wp-block-column">\n<ul><li>Container</li><li>Link</li><li>Team</li><li>Projects</li></ul>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class="wp-block-column">\n<ul><li>Posts</li><li>Featured Posts</li><li>More to come…</li></ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<p>The theme comes with remarkably advanced theme options <g class="gr_ gr_65 gr-alert gr_gramm gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear Grammar only-del replaceWithoutSep" id="65" data-gr-id="65">and it</g> allows you to set up your website as you desire. The page layouts include architecture features to make it easy to build your own website.</p>\n\n\n\n<a href="https://wplook.com/product/themes/business/architect-wordpress-theme/" target="_blank" class="button green-button">Learn More about The Architect</a>\n<a href="https://wplook.com/createa-a-wordpress-site/?utm_source=post&amp;utm_medium=link&amp;utm_campaign=get_theme_free" class="button pink-button" title="Get this theme for FREE">Get this theme for FREE</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Studio 9</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class="wp-block-image shadow"><img src="https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/studio-9.jpg" alt="Studio 9 - WordPress Theme for Photographs" class="wp-image-20673" srcset="https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/studio-9.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/studio-9-300x239.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/studio-9-768x612.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/studio-9-1024x817.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/studio-9-600x479.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /><figcaption>Studio 9 &#8211; WordPress Theme for Photographs</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Studio 9 is another theme compatible with the Gutenberg and WordPress 5.0+. It&#8217;s an elegant and feature-rich WordPress theme perfect for Web Designers, Creative Agencies, Photographs and Freelancers looking to develop a modern online presence using Gutenberg Blocks. This creative theme allows you to introduce your company and your services to your potential clients, showcase your past and on-going projects to your audience in an organized manner and publish articles on your blog. </p>\n\n\n\n<h4 id="mce_10">The&nbsp;theme&nbsp;is&nbsp;coming&nbsp;with&nbsp;8 Gutenberg Blocks</h4>\n\n\n\n<div class="wp-block-columns has-2-columns">\n<div class="wp-block-column">\n<ul><li>Accordion</li><li>Alert</li><li>Text Container</li><li>Pricing Table</li></ul>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class="wp-block-column">\n<ul><li>Container</li><li>Link</li><li>Team</li><li>Projects</li></ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<a href="https://wplook.com/product/themes/business/studio-9-wordpress-theme-for-freelancers/" target="_blank" class="button green-button">Learn More about Studio 9 </a>\n<a href="https://wplook.com/createa-a-wordpress-site/?utm_source=post&amp;utm_medium=link&amp;utm_campaign=get_theme_free" class="button pink-button" title="Get this theme for FREE">Get this theme for FREE</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Neve</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class="wp-block-image shadow"><img src="https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/neve-1024x948.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-28198" srcset="https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/neve-1024x948.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/neve-300x278.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/neve-768x711.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/neve-600x556.jpg 600w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/neve.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /><figcaption>Super Fast, Featherweight Theme to Enter the Gutenberg Era</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Neve is a Gutenberg compatible WordPress theme that comes with a minimalist and content-focused design. This theme gives you all the tools you need to build a professional looking website for any niche. Neve is packed with a lot of customization features and elements that are very easy to use. It is fully compatible with Gutenberg editor, Elementor, Divi, SiteOrigin, Beaver Builder, Brizy and many many more. You can create the website the way you like with its awesome page builder support. This theme is optimized for speed and is also a translation ready theme in order to fulfill our customer’s needs from all around the world. Moreover, with Neve you can get your new website installed and online in under 1 minute! This is one of the best Free Gutenberg WordPress theme.</p>\n\n\n\n<a href="https://themeisle.com/themes/neve/" target="_blank" class="button green-button">Learn More about Neve</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Makenzie</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class="wp-block-image shadow"><img src="https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/makenzie-lifestyle-wordpress-theme-demo.jpg" alt="Make